  "description": "<ul><li>4 - 5 Days / week including 1 weekend (Sat or Sun)</li><li>8.5 hours per day (including 1 hour lunch break)</li><li>Contract Duration: Immediate - Mar 2026</li><li>Salary: $12 / hr (weekdays), $13 / hr (weekend) + Commission</li><li>Location: MBS</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Possess Retail Sales / Beauty experience</li><li>Passion for Fragrance, Makeup or Skincare</li><li>Able to commit 4 - 5 days per week including 1 weekend per week (Sat or Sun)</li></ul><p>To apply please click on the APPLY NOW button or email your resume with the following detail inside your resume for faster processing:</p><p><br /></p><p>• Reason for leaving each past & current employment</p><p>• Salary drawn for each past & current employment</p><p>• Expected Salary</p><p>• Earliest availability date</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified. By submitting any application or résumé to us, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us collecting, using, retaining and disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.</p><p><br /></p><p>Yoong Poh Feng</p><p>EA License | 14C7092</p><p>EA Registration Number | R1105076</p>",
